item.title: new year new me (2022 edition)
item.author: Author
item.description: It was midnight Decemeber 31st 2021. Like always I didn’t do much this year to celebrate it. Most of the time I go to sleep and treat it like any other day, because guess what it is just another day. But this time I had trouble sleeping. Most of the time I close my eyes and let whatever weird fantasy I am having take me away in its beautifull fucked up journey.
